| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-0027 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: c07d5ce2-13ea-5059-a3da-a5dd8e13a9f1"
